Package structs

Package structs provides data structures:
Mypair,
virtual Myset,
MysetTable extending Myset,
MysetDynamic extending MysetTable.

These classes are meant to represent key-value pairs and array-based structures to hold them.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Mypair
    Mypair is a stucture which holds key-value pairs (keys as String, values as double)
    Myset
    Myset is a virtual class representing set
    MysetDynamic
    MysetDynamic is a structure based on arrays which holds only Mypair objects, with a flexible automatic reisizing
    MysetTable
    MysetTable is a structure based on arrays which holds only Mypair objects, with a set and final size
